name: "ACOUSTIC FIRE" EP ALBUM- ( Autographed copy)
description:
Kandace Lindsey's new EP "Acoustic Fire" album.

It is an Organic, Emotional, Vulnerable, and Raw album. 
On this album we just focused on, my voice, the emotion and the groove, verses a big slick production. 
That's why I named this album "Acoustic Fire"

name: KANDACE LINDSEY  (Self-Titled album) CD - ( Autographed copy)
description: Kandace Lindsey's introduction into music industry is finally released. Recorded in 2000, but finally this "vintage" Kandace Lindsey album is available to the public. This was her first hand at songwriting & creating vocal arrangements. Reminiscent of artists like Chaka Kahn, Sade, Erykah Badu,and Amel Larrieux this album is recommended if you appreciate these artists. With her sultry lead vocals & her lush background harmonies, this Sexy Jazzy Soul album will take you on a ride.

name: DESERT CHILD CD  - (Autographed copy)
description:
Rising out of the Phoenix heat, a rebirth of both hot and cool, Kandace Lindsey is currently stirring up her own passionate, hard-hitting blend of Raw Gritty Soulful Rock music. The main ingredient is a voice the likes of which are all too rare these days - bursting with character, personality and fierce skill.

Drawing on a rich range of influences, from Tina Turner and Lenny Kravitz to Sly Stone, Chaka Khan and Alicia Keys.

Kandace's  recordings of her own, "You're No Good","Any Love"," Spend The Night" were featured on several episodes of  'MTV's Real World/Road Rules Challenge & Real World/Road Rules Extreme during the 2003-05 seasons, and in June 2004 Showtime's 'Queer as Folk' show follows suit with "Soul Shuffle".

name: SOUL EXPLORATIONS CD - (Autographed copy)
description: Compilation of Kandace's Lindsey Deep House/Electronica side projects. Kandace expresses herself in many different ways and this is her hand at experimenting in that genre. Let Kandace's Voice Lift You, and Take you To Higher Heights!!!!
